info.name: Tumblr - Doctor Who "Bad Wolf" logo
info.description: "badwolf." to replace the Tumblr logo on your dashboard!
info.additionalInfo: Tested on Firefox only. Please let me know on Tumblr (GeekintheJeep) with any possible alignment issues, questions, or requests! I hope I'm not stepping on any toes by making this when there are other similar versions available. I couldn't find any others that kept an actual link to the Tumblr dashboard in the logo, so I made one myself.
